{
  "texts": [
    "Students noted that not all academics encourage the use of AI in educational contexts, with some academics explicitly forbidding its use for assignments and research.",
    "At present, guidelines regarding the use of AI in academic settings are not fully developed.",
    "This lack of clarity can lead to student confusion due to mixed attitudes and messages about AI in their educational institutions.",
    "Students who disregard these rules risk facing penalties for academic misconduct.",
    "There is a fine line between using AI to assist in learning and engaging in dishonest behaviours during assessments."
  ]
}